[package]
name = "font"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Sebastian Köln <s3bk@protonmail.org>",]
edition = "2018"

[features]
unstable = [ "slotmap/unstable", "tuple/nightly",]
svg = [ "svg_dom", "inflate",]
woff = [ "brotli-decompressor", "inflate",]

[dependencies]
pdf_encoding = "0.4"
nom = "5.1"
log = "0.4"
decorum = "0.3"
itertools = "0.10"
indexmap = "1.9"
istring = "0.3.4"

[dev-dependencies]
walkdir = "2.3"
memmap = "*"

[dependencies.pathfinder_geometry]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder/"

[dependencies.pathfinder_content]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder/"

[dependencies.pathfinder_color]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder/"

[dependencies.tuple]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/tuple/"

[dependencies.rand]
version = "0.7"
features = [ "wasm-bindgen",]

[dependencies.slotmap]
version = "1.0"

[dependencies.brotli-decompressor]
version = "2.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.inflate]
version = "0.4.5"
optional = true

[dependencies.svg_dom]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/svg"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.svg_dom]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/svg"

[dev-dependencies.svg_draw]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/svg"

[dev-dependencies.pathfinder_renderer]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder/"

[dev-dependencies.pathfinder_export]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder/"

[dev-dependencies.env_logger]
version = "*"

[patch."https://github.com/s3bk/svg".svg_dom]
path = "../svg/dom"

[patch."https://github.com/s3bk/svg".svg_draw]
path = "../svg/draw"

[patch."https://github.com/s3bk/svg".svg_text]
path = "../svg/text"

[patch."https://github.com/pdf-rs/font".font]
path = "."

[package]
name = "globalcache"
version = "0.2.2"
edition = "2021"
description = "Cache utility that allows per-process managent of many cache instances"
license = "MIT"

[features]
sync = []
async = [ "tokio",]
global = [ "tokio", "tracing", "once_cell",]

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1.53"
tuple = "0.5.1"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.18.2"
optional = true
features = [ "sync", "rt", "time",]

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.34"
optional = true

[dependencies.once_cell]
version = "1.10.0"
optional = true

[package]
name = "glyphmatcher"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
itertools = "*"
serde_json = "*"

[dependencies.font]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/font"

[dependencies.pdf_encoding]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/encoding"

[dependencies.pathfinder_content]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder/"

[dependencies.pathfinder_geometry]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder/"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "*"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.postcard]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "alloc",]

[dependencies.istring]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/istring"
features = [ "serialize",]

[package]
name = "istring"
version = "0.3.4"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Sebastian Köln <s3bk@protonmail.com>",]
description = "A replacement for String that allows storing short strings of length up to sizeof<String>() - 1 without a heap allocation"
categories = []
license = "MIT"
homepage = "https://github.com/s3bk/istring"
repository = "https://github.com/s3bk/istring"
keywords = [ "string", "inline", "no_std",]

[features]
size = [ "datasize",]
serialize = [ "serde",]
std = []
rkyv = [ "dep:rkyv",]

[dependencies.datasize]
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.rkyv]
version = "0.7"
optional = true
default-features = false

[package]
name = "pathfinder_resources"
version = "0.5.0"
edition = "2018"
authors = [ "Patrick Walton <pcwalton@mimiga.net>",]
description = "Shaders, textures, etc. for the Pathfinder vector graphics library"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"
homepage = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"

[dependencies]

[[example]]
name = "content"

[[example]]
name = "metadata"

[[example]]
name = "names"

[[example]]
name = "read"

[[example]]
name = "other_page_content"

[package]
name = "pdf"
version = "0.9.0"
authors = [ "Erlend Langseth <3rlendhl@gmail.com>", "Sebastian Köln <s3bk@protonmail.com>",]
repository = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/pdf"
readme = "../README.md"
keywords = [ "pdf",]
license = "MIT"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/pdf"
edition = "2018"
description = "PDF reader"

[features]
mmap = [ "memmap2",]
dump = [ "tempfile",]
threads = [ "jpeg-decoder/default",]
sync = []
cache = [ "globalcache",]
default = [ "sync", "cache",]

[dependencies]
snafu = "0.7.1"
libflate = "2.0.0"
deflate = "1.0.0"
itertools = "0.10.0"
weezl = "0.1.4"
once_cell = "1.5.2"
log = "0.4.14"
md5 = "0.7"
aes = "0.8.2"
cbc = "0.1"
stringprep = "0.1.2"
sha2 = "0.10.2"
fax = "0.2.0"
bitflags = "1.3"
datasize = "0.2.13"
indexmap = "2.1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
glob = "0.3.0"

[lib]
doctest = false

[dependencies.pdf_derive]
version = "0.2.0"
path = "../pdf_derive"

[dependencies.memmap2]
version = "0.5.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.tempfile]
version = "3.2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.jpeg-decoder]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.euclid]
version = "0.22.7"
optional = true

[dependencies.istring]
version = "0.3.3"
features = [ "std", "size",]

[dependencies.globalcache]
version = "0.2.2"
features = [ "sync",]
optional = true

[package]
name = "pdf_derive"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Erlend Langseth <3rlendhl@gmail.com>", "Sebastian Köln <s3bk@protonmail.com>",]
homepage = "https://github.com/pdf-rs"
repository = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/pdf_derive"
description = "helper for pdf-rs."
license = "MIT"
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0.24"
quote = "1"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies.syn]
version = "1"
features = [ "full", "extra-traits",]

[package]
name = "pdf_encoding"
version = "0.4.0"
authors = [ "Sebastian Köln <s3bk@protonmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
license = "BSD-3-Clause"
description = "Font related encodings"
homepage = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/encoding"
repository = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/encoding"
readme = "README.md"
include = [ "agl-aglfn/glyphlist.txt", "src", "build.rs", "README.md",]
exclude = [ "encodings",]

[dependencies]
lazy_static = "1.4"

[[bench]]
name = "render"
harness = false

[package]
name = "pdf_render"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Sebastian Köln <s3bk@protonmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"

[features]
unstable = []

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
pdf_encoding = "0.4"
itertools = "*"
image = "0.24.2"
instant = "*"
custom_debug_derive = "*"
once_cell = "*"
serde_json = "*"

[dev-dependencies]
criterion = "0.3"
env_logger = "*"

[dependencies.pdf]
default-features = false
features = [ "cache", "dump",]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/pdf"

[dependencies.pathfinder_renderer]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"

[dependencies.pathfinder_color]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"

[dependencies.pathfinder_geometry]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"

[dependencies.pathfinder_resources]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"

[dependencies.pathfinder_content]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"

[dependencies.font]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/font"

[dependencies.globalcache]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/cachelib"
features = [ "sync",]

[dependencies.istring]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/istring"

[dependencies.glyphmatcher]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/glyphmatcher"

[package]
name = "surfman"
license = "MIT / Apache-2.0"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Patrick Walton <pcwalton@mimiga.net>", "Emilio Cobos Álvarez <emilio@crisal.io>", "The Servo Project Developers",]
description = "A cross-platform, low-level toolkit for GPU surface management"
repository = "https://github.com/servo/surfman"
build = "build.rs"

[build-dependencies]
gl_generator = "0.13"
cfg_aliases = "0.1.0"

[features]
default = [ "sm-winit",]
sm-angle = []
sm-angle-builtin = [ "mozangle",]
sm-angle-default = [ "sm-angle",]
sm-no-wgl = [ "sm-angle-default",]
sm-test = []
sm-wayland-default = []
sm-winit = [ "winit",]
sm-x11 = [ "x11",]
sm-raw-window-handle = [ "raw-window-handle",]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.1"
lazy_static = "1"
libc = "0.2"
log = "0.4"
parking_lot = "0.9"

[dev-dependencies]
clap = "2"
gl = "0.13"
png = "0.15"
rand = "0.7"

[dependencies.euclid]
version = "0.20"
features = []

[dependencies.osmesa-sys]
version = "0.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.winit]
version = "<0.19.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.raw-window-handle]
version = "0.3.3"
optional = true

[target.x86_64-apple-darwin.dependencies]
cgl = "0.3.2"
cocoa = "0.19"
core-foundation = "0.6"
core-graphics = "0.17"
display-link = "0.2"
io-surface = "0.12"
mach = "0.3"
metal = "0.17"
objc = "0.2"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies]
wio = "0.2"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"macos\", target_os = \"android\"))))".dependencies.wayland-sys]
version = "0.24"
features = [ "client", "dlopen", "egl",]

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os = \"macos\", target_os = \"android\"))))".dependencies.x11]
version = "2.3.0"
features = [ "xlib",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.mozangle]
version = "0.2"
features = [ "egl",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "d3d11", "wingdi", "winuser", "libloaderapi",]

[package]
name = "tuple"
version = "0.5.2"
authors = [ "Sebastian Köln <s3bk@protonmail.com>",]
description = "Element-wise operations on tuples"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/tuple"
homepage = "https://github.com/s3bk/tuple.git"
repository = "https://github.com/s3bk/tuple.git"
keywords = [ "tuple", "science",]
license = "MIT"

[features]
default = [ "impl_num", "impl_serde", "std",]
impl_num = [ "num-traits",]
impl_simd = [ "nightly",]
impl_serde = [ "serde",]
std = []
nightly = []

[dependencies.num-traits]
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/pdf-rs/font"]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/font"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/s3bk/cachelib"]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/cachelib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/s3bk/glyphmatcher"]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/glyphmatcher"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/s3bk/istring"]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/istring"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"]
git = "https://github.com/servo/pathfinder"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/pdf-rs/pdf"]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/pdf"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/pdf-rs/encoding"]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/encoding"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/pdf-rs/pdf_render"]
git = "https://github.com/pdf-rs/pdf_render"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/servo/surfman"]
git = "https://github.com/servo/surfman"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "f3df871ac8c3926fe9106d86a3e51e20aa50d3cc"

[source."https://github.com/s3bk/tuple"]
git = "https://github.com/s3bk/tuple"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
